<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>RubriCheck AI | Questions</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/images/RubriCheck%20Logo.png">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <header class="site-header">
    <div class="container nav-bar">
      <a class="brand" href="/" aria-label="RubriCheck AI home">
        <img class="brand-logo" src="/images/RubriCheck%20Logo.png" alt="RubriCheck AI logo">
        <span class="brand-name">Rubri<span>Check</span> <small>AI</small></span>
      </a>

      <nav class="main-nav" aria-label="Main navigation">
        <a class="nav-link" href="/">Home</a>
        <a class="nav-link" href="/dashboard">Dashboard</a>
        <a class="nav-link" href="/upload">New Review</a>
      </nav>

      <div class="auth-area" aria-label="Account actions">
        <button class="login-button" type="button" data-login-open>Log In</button>

        <a class="user-chip hidden" href="/dashboard" aria-label="Open user dashboard" data-user-chip>
          <span class="user-icon">DS</span>
          <span>Demo Student</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="modal-overlay hidden" data-login-modal>
    <section class="login-modal" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="login-title">
      <button class="modal-close" type="button" aria-label="Close login" data-login-close>&times;</button>

      <img class="modal-logo" src="/images/RubriCheck%20Logo.png" alt="RubriCheck AI logo">
      <h2 id="login-title">Log in to RubriCheck AI</h2>
      <p>This is a frontend demo login. No real account or password is needed yet.</p>

      <form class="login-form">
        <label for="demo-email">Email</label>
        <input id="demo-email" type="email" value="student@myrp.edu.sg" readonly>

        <label for="demo-password">Password</label>
        <input id="demo-password" type="password" value="password" readonly>

        <button class="btn btn-primary" type="button" data-demo-login>Use Demo Login</button>
      </form>
    </section>
  </div>

  <main class="questions-page">
    <section class="questions-shell container">
      <div class="questions-header">
        <div>
          <p class="questions-kicker">Business Analytics Report - Q2 2025</p>
          <h1>Lecturer Question Prep</h1>
          <p>Practise possible presentation and viva questions generated from your assignment review.</p>
        </div>

        <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/feedback">Back to Feedback Report</a>
      </div>

      <section class="question-summary-card">
        <div class="question-summary-icon" aria-hidden="true">AI</div>
        <div>
          <h2>AI-generated viva questions</h2>
          <p>These questions are generated from your assignment, methodology, and identified gaps. Practise answering them out loud before your presentation.</p>
          <dl>
            <div>
              <dt>Assignment</dt>
              <dd>Business Analytics Report</dd>
            </div>
            <div>
              <dt>Readiness Score</dt>
              <dd>78%</dd>
            </div>
            <div>
              <dt>Focus Areas</dt>
              <dd>Explanation depth, evidence, conclusion clarity</dd>
            </div>
          </dl>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="questions-toolbar">
        <strong><span data-question-count>6</span> questions generated</strong>
        <button class="regenerate-button" type="button" data-regenerate-questions>Regenerate Questions</button>
      </div>

      <section class="question-list" data-question-list aria-label="AI-generated lecturer questions">
        <article class="question-card">
          <span class="question-number">1</span>
          <div>
            <div class="question-meta">
              <span>Analysis</span>
              <em>Medium</em>
            </div>
            <h2>Why did you choose this approach for your analysis?</h2>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="question-card">
          <span class="question-number">2</span>
          <div>
            <div class="question-meta">
              <span>Rubric</span>
              <em>Hard</em>
            </div>
            <h2>How does your solution meet the rubric criteria?</h2>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="question-card">
          <span class="question-number">3</span>
          <div>
            <div class="question-meta">
              <span>Evidence</span>
              <em>Easy</em>
            </div>
            <h2>What evidence supports your main findings?</h2>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="question-card">
          <span class="question-number">4</span>
          <div>
            <div class="question-meta">
              <span>Reflection</span>
              <em>Medium</em>
            </div>
            <h2>What limitations did you identify in your assignment?</h2>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="question-card">
          <span class="question-number">5</span>
          <div>
            <div class="question-meta">
              <span>Improvement</span>
              <em>Medium</em>
            </div>
            <h2>How would you improve your work if given more time?</h2>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="question-card">
          <span class="question-number">6</span>
          <div>
            <div class="question-meta">
              <span>Conclusion</span>
              <em>Hard</em>
            </div>
            <h2>How does your conclusion link back to your objectives?</h2>
          </div>
        </article>
      </section>

      <section class="questions-cta">
        <span aria-hidden="true">★</span>
        <h2>Ready to review another assignment?</h2>
        <p>Upload a new assignment draft and rubric to get another AI-powered review.</p>
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/upload">Review another assignment</a>
      </section>
    </section>
  </main>

  <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
